    • JTestBench

      public JTestBench(long inSeed, JBloomType inBloomType, JGridSysType inGridSysType, JSkipListType inSkipListType, byte inStartPower, byte inEndPower)
      A proper constructor for a JTestBench object instantiation.
      Parameters:
      inSeed - (long) Seed for the Random
      inBloomType - (JBloomType) Which Bloom Filter implementation to use
      inGridSysType - (JGridSysType) Which Coordinate System to use: GARS or MGRS
      inSkipListType - (JSkipListType) Which Skip List implementation to use
      inStartPowerOf10 - (byte) Starting (i.e. smallest) size, in power of 10, of The Data Set and Test Set during the Test Bench run
      inEndPowerOf10 - (byte) Ending (i.e. the largest) size, in power of 10, of The Data Set and Test Set during the Test Bench run
